   THE STORY OF PRIME MINISTER MARGARET THATCHER
  </a>
  <a href="#2" id="2">
   Thatcher's friends all over the world had reckoned without the British Conservative Party, which had looked at the opinion polls, the bad economic news and an unpopular new tax and smelled a loss at the next election.
  </a>
